 CHT International ICT Total Solution will feature the theme of "Green Sustainability". We are not only able to provide International communication and transmission circuits, but also ICT projects, voice and video communication value-added service, achieving a one-stop ICT service shopping for customers.
	With complete network topology of submarine and terrestrial cables worldwide, satellite resources, global operation, combination of hard power and soft power integrated solutions, we strive to enhance our ability to better serve...More
 CHT International ICT Total Solution will feature the theme of "Green Sustainability". We are not only able to provide International communication and transmission circuits, but also ICT projects, voice and video communication value-added service, achieving a one-stop ICT service shopping for customers.
	With complete network topology of submarine and terrestrial cables worldwide, satellite resources, global operation, combination of hard power and soft power integrated solutions, we strive to enhance our ability to better serve the needs of our customers for internationally collaborated operations while reducing their costs in helping them achieve sustainability for their business operations.Less





















